":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9f506b653c02ae4790c184fdb96e65821c324fb","tid":1697913,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b55ade06b0b9221a9d27dd7a3cc57c570368f2","tid":1697913,"uid":274149,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"組工會，全民三罷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:00:49.000Z","msg":"連遊行都開始少人，罷工好難夠人參與<br />\n只會露出底牌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救，唔係因為人多，所以先行動，<br />\n係要反抗所以行動"},{"pid":"d1b38efecb9a45672f7119c38e03520902baa715","tid":1697913,"uid":257190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"致樓主<br />\n<br />\n有大把嘢可以做<br />\n1. 每晚十點大嗌<br />\n2. 先係每星期四買黃店，之後日日買，創造黃色經濟圈<br />\n3. 星期六日有集會就出<br />\n4. 打twitter國際戰<br />\n5. 捐錢，唔理你捐612，星火，定教會<br />\n6. 做文宣<br />\n7. 練跑"},{"pid":"3ada11ae54bd55b65a39453b936e693bc894915e","tid":1697913,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:05:59.000Z","msg":"唔係想放負 不過何妖單野 加上之前吹風<br />\n覺得垃圾政府出手段延期/取消區選<br />\n或者直接加1更多鐵票/做手腳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ea25a0580fca787a82791569919f3cc1cdde68","tid":1697913,"uid":257190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"Be water去打仗，<br />\n由只打星期六日，變到每日都打，罷買藍店，<br />\n爆買黃店，你幫襯左光時未？<br />\n唔太方便比錢買嘢嘅，你每晚大嗌左未？"},{"pid":"d52c443288e19388e23ca99105090d17a9b0bbe0","tid":1697913,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2cf4a800b41813214fdfc84174c6358ed5191f9","tid":1697913,"uid":257190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9f506b653c02ae4790c184fdb96e65821c324fb","tid":1697913,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b55ade06b0b9221a9d27dd7a3cc57c570368f2","tid":1697913,"uid":274149,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"組工會，全民三罷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:00:49.000Z","msg":"連遊行都開始少人，罷工好難夠人參與<br />\n只會